headline: Cboe Global Markets Declares Second-Quarter 2025 Dividend
summary: Cboe Global Markets, Inc. (Cboe: CBOE), the world's leading derivatives and securities exchange network, today announced its Board of Directors has declared a quarterly cash dividend of $0.63 per share of common stock for the second quarter of 2025. The second-quarter 2025 dividend is payable on June 13, 2025, to stockholders of record as of May 30, 2025.
